  FWIW.  There really are cases where engine oil in the gearbox
> is the right thing.

Some of the Mercedes and Volvo MANUAL trannies called for ATF. Shoot, VW
has 4 different types of anti-freeze formulas for their various engines
through the years. Never assume, consult your owner's manual for correct
specs AND type of lube/fluid or risk poor results.
